column5: what happened to tuesday chat?everytime i,ve tried no one is there.on anyday.
I'm usually in there Tues nights...Ironically the only other person I've chatted to recently was Rapala Boy.LOL

A lot of the regular voices are gone. Me? I'm too busy brewing up salsa most Tuesday evenings to sit online for any length of time. Heck, yesterday was the first time fishing in 3 weeks. Now a day behind.
